                    <app loc="lines 1-2"><note>Torremuzza, Ferrara: Εὐαίριος; Franz: Εὐκαίριος; Kaibel, Ferrua, Agnello, Wessel: Εὐάγριος</note></app>
                    <app loc="line 3"><note>Franz: μου; Torremuzza, Kaibel, Wessel: ἐμοῦ; Ferrua: μοι; Ferrara, Agnello, Korhonen, lapis: ἐμοί</note></app>
                    <app loc="line 5"><note>Κωπάντις lapis, Torremuzza, Ferrara; Franz: Κωτιαν<corr>ης</corr>; Kaibel, Ferrua, Agnello, Wessel; Korhonen: Κω<corr>στ</corr>αντίς</note></app>
                </listApp>
